    <id>https://yinghu.netlify.app/posts/e3afeac7.html</id>
    <published>2024-05-22T04:24:26.000Z</published>
    <updated>2024-05-22T04:25:33.528Z</updated>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<link rel="stylesheet" class="aplayer-secondary-style-marker" href="\assets\css\APlayer.min.css"><script src="\assets\js\APlayer.min.js" class="aplayer-secondary-script-marker"></script><p>仅凭双目交汇，便能捕捉到对方记忆的少女</p><p>将被涂满深红的恶心人偶当做双亲而一同生活的青梅竹马</p><p>只用微笑就能操纵人心、体弱多病的妹妹</p><p>与不知何处有缺陷的少女们相遇，被卷入不可思议事件中的主人公</p><p>那仿佛用手指描绘的昔日记忆一般，一点一点将他的心给侵蚀</p><p>痛苦而又令人怀念，记忆的物语……</p><p><img src="https://r2.touchgal.net/2023/05/s7JNev5j-wallpaper_pc-1024x576.jpg"></img></p><hr><a class="btn-beautify " href="http://111.173.104.54:5244/d/%E6%A2%93%E6%BE%AA%E5%A6%99%E5%A6%99%E5%B1%8B%EF%BC%88zi0.cc%EF%BC%89%E7%9A%84%E8%B5%84%E6%BA%90(gal%E5%A4%9A%EF%BC%8C%E6%8E%A8%E8%8D%90)/%60%E3%80%90%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%E3%80%91/%E6%B1%89%E5%8C%96galgame%E4%BC%9A%E7%A4%BE%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86/%E6%B1%89%E5%8C%96%E4%BC%9A%E7%A4%BE%E5%90%88%E9%9B%86%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%20part7/cutlass/%5B111105%5D%5Bcutlass%5D%20NOeSIS%EF%BD%9E%E5%98%98%E3%82%92%E5%90%90%E3%81%84%E3%81%9F%E8%A8%98%E6%86%B6%E3%81%AE%E7%89%A9%E8%AA%9E%EF%BD%9E.rar"   title="点击下载"><i class="red larger"></i><span>点击下载</span></a>]]></content>
    
    
      
      
